function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)	
--	-- Play victory music
--	Hydra.MusicOverride("Kehj_Hell", "Music_WorldBoss_Ashava_EndVictory");
	-- Clear Weather override for Ashava fight
	Hydra.ClearWeatherOverride(Hydra.ReferenceWorld("Kehj_Hell"))
	
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA);
	
	local tHoradrim = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Battlefield_Ashava_Horadrim");
	
	if (#tHoradrim > 0) then
		for i, idHoradrim in ipairs(tHoradrim) do
			Hydra.ActorOverrideAIAwarenessRadius(idHoradrim, 0, false);
			Hydra.ActorOverrideAIAwarenessRadius(idHoradrim, 0, true);
		end
	end
	
		------------------------------------------------------
	-- First Time Rewards
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Ashava", idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Ashava")
	end
	
	------------------------------------------------------
	
end
